info.description: ITK is an open-source, cross-platform library that provides developers with an extensive suite of software tools for image analysis. This package implements anisotropic diffusion using Lattice Basis Reduction. For more information, see  Mirebeau J., Fehrenbach J., Risser L., Tobji S. "Anisotropic Diffusion in ITK" http://insight-journal.org/browse/publication/953 http://hdl.handle.net/10380/3505
info.name: itk-anisotropicdiffusionlbr
info.summary: Smooth images while preserving edges or coherent structures.
